name: Tree Terminator
description:
Tree Terminator

The game that is a game.

Information
  • The Tree-Upgrade will increase the amount of points gained for every automatic click.
  • The Axe-Upgrade will increase the amount of points gained for every human click.
  • The Fire-Upgrade will increase the automatic tick rate.

! The game automatically saves every 15 seconds and whenever you buy something !

! L-Ctrl + L-Shift + L will Reset your save file !
